CRMD WE ARE SO LPAD LPAD is the fastest and smartest way to get NDA approved FDA actually wants more companies to utilize LPAD pathway We will be number 2 for them Heres a quote from the last meeting with the FDA the FDA agreed that the company could request consideration of Neutrolin for approval under the LPAD Pathway For those of you who are not familiar with LPAD it stands for Limited Population Pathway for Antimicrobial and Antifungal Drugs We are very pleased about this outcome What this means for Neutrolin is that if the FDA agrees to grant LPAD status the FDA will have approaches for streamlined development and regulatory flexibility regarding the evidence required to support drug approval for patient populations with serious disease and limited or no treatment options while still meeting appropriate standards for safety and effectiveness including fewer or shorter clinical trials
